input_args.query: 'Is the query "If I purchase something online, can I return it in store" accurately addressed by the response "Yes, you can return an item purchased online to a lululemon store. According to our Returns page (https://shop.lululemon.com/help/returns), if you’re having second thoughts about your purchase, and it was made within 30 days, you can return it! You can also track your order or return here (https://shop.lululemon.com/help/track-order.). If you have any other questions, please reach out to our Guest Education Centre (GEC) by Live Chat, Apple Messages, phone or email. Phone number: 1.877.263.9300 | Hours: 6am – 6pm PT on weekdays, 6am – 4pm PT on weekends. You can find more information on our Contact Us page (https://shop.lululemon.com/contact)." ? Kindly answer with either "Yes" or "No".'
